divs: sighting detailsi am writing to you to inform mufon of a rock art site (rochester creek utah) that is a definite native american depiction of a ufo crash site and possible alien recovery operation. i can send along pics of the site (petroglyphs) with my notes attached. i have been a student of rock art for over 30 years and have visited over 300 sites. i would like these pics to be submitteed to someone at mufon that knows and has experience in this area as this is very hard evidence and can be readily studied. i am concerned that the site could be comprimissed through a rush to the site by the public. awaiting your reply so i can send along these images\report.
Summary: 700 year old petroglyph (Fremont culture) depicting ufo crash site
